cc:Work.dc:title: transformation matrix values for dimetry xy, xz, yz planes
cc:Work.dc:description:
If these values are used as transformation values on shapes, they will be distorted as they were drawn on xy, xz, or yz planes. 
Hope there are no mistakes in it, I didn\'t find any. 
 
To my experience the transformation matrix alone cannot produce accurate result in inkscape.
